parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID to conduct user registration to successfully

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is a 10-digit ms timestamp of the request

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: This is authorization certificate for API provided by API platform. The life span for authentication file is 24 hours, and it's invalid if it times out

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Signature generated by partner_id, spi_path, timestamp, access_token, sign_method. The HMAC-SHA256 encryption algorithm is recommended.

parameters.name: address_id
parameters.description: The identify of address you want to delete

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for your tracing

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Include error info if API error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Include error detail info if API error. Empty if no error happened

notes: The documentation includes error codes section with various logistics and general error codes, and an API permissions section at the bottom. The image shows full request/response examples and error examples in JSON format.
